
## Installing

xcode-select --install
npm install node-gyp -g
brew install giflib cairo libjpeg giflib pixman
npm install canvas

### Install MongoDB to keep card settings

brew install mongodb
mkdir -p /data/db
sudo chmod 0755 /data/db
sudo chown $USER /data/db
mongod  (in a term window)

### Notes: Using Fabric or Kanva to render ###
Fabric looks like a slightly better library, but is not working with node-canvas 2.0, so switched to Kanva instead.
Fabric is supposed to work if using canvas@1.6.11 but I couldn't get anything to render, so removed it
